            "name": "sectionType",
            "description": "Filter by section type.\nCMS_SECTION_TYPE_UNSPECIFIED (0) means \"show all types\" (no filter).\n\n - CMS_SECTION_TYPE_UNSPECIFIED: Default unspecified value.\n - CMS_SECTION_TYPE_HERO: Hero banner section at the top of the landing page.\n - CMS_SECTION_TYPE_FEATURE: Feature card section highlighting platform capabilities.\n - CMS_SECTION_TYPE_FAQ: FAQ accordion section with questions and answers.\n - CMS_SECTION_TYPE_TESTIMONIAL: Testimonial/quote section from users or stakeholders.\n - CMS_SECTION_TYPE_CTA: Call-to-action section with button.\n - CMS_SECTION_TYPE_CUSTOM: Custom freeform section.",
